== About ==
This is a very simple script to change the background picture of gnome.
The wallpapers are downloaded from National Geographic's official site,
i.e. the photo of the day column. The copyright of photos downloaded belongs
to the National Geographic. Do not abuse it. More info can be obtained from:
    http://photography.nationalgeographic.com/photography/photo-of-the-day

== Scripts ==
crontab -l | { cat; echo "0 0 * * * /dir/to/main.py > /dev/null"; } | crontab -

